      <strong>Quick answer:</strong> Berberine is clinically proven to benefit at least 9 health conditions. The strongest evidence supports its use for blood sugar regulation (reduces fasting glucose by 20-30%), cholesterol management (lowers LDL by 20-25%), and weight management through GLP-1 activation. The standard dosage is 500mg taken 2-3 times daily with meals. Berberine has demonstrated comparable efficacy to metformin in head-to-head clinical trials.
