      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="zap" size={22} /></div>
        <h3>AMPK Activation</h3>
        <p>Berberine activates AMP-activated protein kinase — the same "metabolic master switch" targeted by metformin and activated by exercise. AMPK regulates glucose metabolism, fat storage, and cellular energy production.</p>
      </div>
